Hi Kristen,
> +				if (pass)
> +					if (dev->subordinate)
> +						pci_bus_size_bridges(dev->subordinate);
How about doing as follows. This also satisfies 80 columns rule.
	if (pass && dev->subordinate)
		pci_bus_size_bridges(dev->subordinate);
Thanks,
Kenji Kaneshige
